<h5 id="subject_608210">
<a href="?PHPSESSID=beafa1c534fcf9df69eac007353a5cfd&amp;topic=52638.msg608210#msg608210" rel="nofollow">Re: [死坑复燃][140122更新]剑世界2.0 规则书1 龟速慢坑</a>
</h5>
<div class="zh_convert" style="float:right;display:none">
[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_608210'));undefined;">繁</a>
<a href="javascript:convertToSimplified (document.getElementById('msg_608210'));undefined;">简</a>]</div>
<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong>回帖 #25 于:</strong> 2014-02-10, 周一 01:42:12 &#187;</div>
<div id="msg_608210_quick_mod"></div>
</div>
